ESP32 Transmitter Pin Connections
1. SX1278 LoRa Module
SX1278 Pin	ESP32 Pin
VCC	3.3V (Do NOT use 5V)
GND	GND
SCK	GPIO18
MISO	GPIO19
MOSI	GPIO23
NSS (CS)	GPIO5
RST	GPIO14
DIO0	GPIO2

⚠️ Place a 470 µF electrolytic capacitor across the LoRa module's 3.3V and GND pins to improve stability.

