Complete Transmitter Wiring Summary
Device	ESP32 GPIO
Good Tank TRIG	GPIO4
Good Tank ECHO	GPIO34
Salt Tank TRIG	GPIO32
Salt Tank ECHO	GPIO35
LoRa NSS (CS)	GPIO5
LoRa SCK	GPIO18
LoRa MISO	GPIO19
LoRa MOSI	GPIO23
LoRa RST	GPIO14
LoRa DIO0	GPIO2
Important Wiring Notes
✅ All grounds must be connected together (ESP32, LoRa, sensors, and power supply).
✅ Power the JSN-SR04T modules from 5V.
✅ Power the SX1278 module only from 3.3V.
✅ Use a 1 kΩ / 2 kΩ voltage divider on each ECHO pin before connecting to GPIO34 and GPIO35.
✅ Add a 470 µF capacitor across the LoRa module's 3.3V and GND to help prevent communication issues due to voltage dips.

